views.text: Using Uber promotions | Bikes & Scooters - Uber Help

You can pay for Lime bikes or scooters with a credit or debit card. You can also add promo codes to your account, which automatically apply the discount to the next qualifying trip.

To add a bike or scooter promo code to your account:

1. Open the Uber app.
2. Tap the menu icon to open the main menu.
3. Select Wallet and scroll down to Promotions.
4. Tap "Add Promo Code."
5. Enter the code and tap "Add".

When you have multiple promo codes available on your account, you can't select which promo applies to your trip. The maximum discount available is automatically applied.

NOTE: Ride promos can't be applied to bike or scooter trips.

To review promo codes on your account:

1. Open the Uber app.
2. Tap the menu icon to open the main menu.
3. Select Wallet and then Promotions. For each promo code on your account, you'll see its expiration date and applicable areas, such as a specific country or city.
